item.description:
Hey Incubators!!!

Time for a last night out with your friends at the incubator before the clock strikes 12.

We'll be hitting up The Cheesecake Factory at the Prudential Center tomorrow night! I figure it was a good place with wide variety of food for everyone. Plus there's free bread, free bread that's wicked delicious, lol.

Note that I've pushed the time back to allow a little more time to get there.

We'll do some quick improvising while they get our table ready too.

I hope you you can make it!!!!

Rock on!

Jason J.
